the new L.

28
00:01:41,436 --> 00:01:43,396
Members of
the Japanese Task force:

29
00:01:44,022 --> 00:01:49,736
Was there ever a time when
the Second L was thought to be Kira?

30
00:01:50,236 --> 00:01:53,406
<i>Near... I've got to kill him!</i>

31
00:01:54,741 --> 00:01:57,201
Bad news!
Demegawa's on TV and...

32
00:01:57,702 --> 00:02:00,663
I, Demegawa, along with
my comrades have finally pinpointed

33
00:02:00,747 --> 00:02:02,415
the location of and surrounded...

34
00:02:02,498 --> 00:02:07,253
the hideout of the evil organization
that is trying to catch our god, Kira.

35
00:02:08,212 --> 00:02:11,215
TRANSFER

36
00:02:28,858 --> 00:02:34,030
<i>Fellow Kira followers!
Do not rush in all at once.</i>

37
00:02:34,405 --> 00:02:37,992
<i>The traitors may hide
among you to escape.</i>

38
00:02:38,618 --> 00:02:44,248
I am Kira's voice.
Follow me and we will corner them...

39
00:02:44,332 --> 00:02:47,210
Place them in front of the cameras...

40
00:02:47,293 --> 00:02:49,253
And offer them to Kira!

41
00:02:57,595 --> 00:02:59,305
I'm not going to miss them!

42
00:03:01,683 --> 00:03:04,686
Near, you have to get out of there.

43
00:03:04,769 --> 00:03:07,855
You have some nerve saying that...
being Kira.

44
00:03:08,314 --> 00:03:10,149
You're still saying that?

45
00:03:10,942 --> 00:03:13,736
There are other organizations
that are chasing Kira.

46
00:03:13,945 --> 00:03:17,323
We get attacked as soon
as I begin to suspect you.

47
00:03:17,657 --> 00:03:19,325
The timing is too convenient.

48
00:03:20,326 --> 00:03:24,038
Near, you've made some kind of mistake
and are making too many assumptions.

49
00:03:24,831 --> 00:03:26,916
Members of the task force...

50
00:03:27,250 --> 00:03:30,461
<i>Kira is probably among you.</i>

51
00:03:30,962 --> 00:03:32,630
<i>Think carefully.</i>

52
00:03:35,299 --> 00:03:36,551
<i>"Light is Kira..."</i>

53
00:03:37,176 --> 00:03:39,262
<i>My suspicions are
getting stronger again...</i>

54
00:03:40,138 --> 00:03:43,391
<i>The former L also
thought that Light was Kira...</i>

55
00:03:51,482 --> 00:03:53,067
The first wave of twenty people will...

56
00:03:53,151 --> 00:03:55,987
break the door and get inside!
The second wave will stand by!

57
00:03:57,780 --> 00:04:00,074
Idiot, out of the way!
We're the first wave!

58
00:04:00,158 --> 00:04:02,201
What?! We're going first!

59
00:04:05,538 --> 00:04:07,790
Near, we've got to
get away immediately.

60
00:04:08,207 --> 00:04:10,126
They're really such foolish people.

61
00:04:11,335 --> 00:04:14,839
I'm not surprised that there are
people who follow Kira.

62
00:04:15,673 --> 00:04:22,889
Since they hope that Kira
will bring justice to evildoers.

63
00:04:23,055 --> 00:04:26,309
The people who are storming
in here are different.

64
00:04:26,392 --> 00:04:28,269
They really are worthless people...

65
00:04:28,561 --> 00:04:31,898
Selfish people...
who only want to have some fun.

66
00:04:33,399 --> 00:04:36,152
I know that, but right now...

67
00:04:36,277 --> 00:04:39,822
Let's use L's fortune and
the Anti-Kira people we hired.

68
00:04:41,157 --> 00:04:43,534
But if we carry out that plan once...

69
00:04:43,618 --> 00:04:46,496
Let's do it.
We should be all ready prepared.

70
00:04:47,497 --> 00:04:48,915
It should be interesting...

71
00:05:06,265 --> 00:05:07,850
M-M...

72
00:05:08,810 --> 00:05:11,312
It's money!!

73
00:05:19,737 --> 00:05:21,280
It's money!

74
00:05:21,864 --> 00:05:22,990
<i>Money?</i>

75
00:05:23,074 --> 00:05:24,408
Wow! So much!

76
00:05:25,117 --> 00:05:26,202
Amazing...

77
00:05:26,619 --> 00:05:28,663
I wish I were there.

78
00:05:28,746 --> 00:05:29,622
Matsuda...

79
00:05:29,705 --> 00:05:32,208
Jeez. Humans are sure interesting.

80
00:05:32,416 --> 00:05:36,712
Well, that can buy apples.
So I kind of understand.

81
00:05:36,796 --> 00:05:38,965
<i>- Igrabbed these first!
- Cut it out!</i>

82
00:05:39,048 --> 00:05:40,049
Out of the way!

83
00:05:40,341 --> 00:05:42,385
<i>Damn. Curse you, Near!</i>

84
00:05:42,468 --> 00:05:44,303
<i>He plans to use
this chaos to escape!</i>

85
00:05:44,804 --> 00:05:46,973
<i>But then he'll be caught on
Demegawa's cameras...</i>

86
00:05:50,601 --> 00:05:54,188
Pilot! Go to the floor where
the money is coming from!

87
00:05:54,856 --> 00:05:57,275
Oh man. What is Deme doing?!

88
00:05:57,358 --> 00:05:59,819
You can't buy love and peace
with money!

89
00:06:02,363 --> 00:06:05,408
<i>A large flurry of money is causing
a panic in Lower Manhattan.</i>

90
00:06:05,992 --> 00:06:07,118
<i>It's the police!</i>

91
00:06:07,285 --> 00:06:08,578
<i>The police?!</i>

92
00:06:08,870 --> 00:06:11,372
<i>As you see they were called in
to contain this chaos!</i>

93
00:06:12,290 --> 00:06:13,749
<i>This is bad. . .at this rate...</i>

94
00:06:18,546 --> 00:06:19,547
Let's go.

95
00:06:20,298 --> 00:06:23,384
Right now, we can just walk out
the entrance.

96
00:06:23,885 --> 00:06:27,346
As expected, the police have to
take action in a riot like this.

97
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:30,099
<i>Damn it... They were prepared
for something like this...</i>

98
00:06:30,474 --> 00:06:32,518
<i>They plan to come out
disguised amongst the police!</i>

99
00:06:33,060 --> 00:06:35,062
<i>Telling Aizawa and the others
to watch over the police</i>

100
00:06:35,146 --> 00:06:37,148
<i>is like saying that I'm Kira!</i>

101
00:06:37,732 --> 00:06:39,817
<i>The police have come out
from the building.</i>

102
00:06:43,404 --> 00:06:44,363
<i>Where is he?!</i>

103
00:06:44,780 --> 00:06:46,073
<i>He should be among them...</i>

104
00:06:46,532 --> 00:06:47,533
<i>Where?!</i>

105
00:06:58,210 --> 00:06:59,712
<i>Damn it...</i>

106
00:07:24,195 --> 00:07:26,739
I wonder how much money that was...

107
00:07:26,822 --> 00:07:27,782
Matsuda...

108
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:30,201
it was probably
about 10 million dollars...

109
00:07:30,409 --> 00:07:31,535
How many apples is that?

110
00:07:40,252 --> 00:07:41,253
Near!

111
00:07:41,462 --> 00:07:42,838
Near?!

112
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:46,801
<i>This is Near.</i>

113
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:52,223
We've reestablished a connection,

114
00:07:52,306 --> 00:07:53,808
so I decided I should give you a call.

115
00:07:54,433 --> 00:07:56,352
<i>Near, you're safe.</i>

116
00:07:56,769 --> 00:07:58,521
Members of the task force...

117
00:07:58,938 --> 00:08:02,942
I think it's about time that you have
some certainty about who Kira is.

118
00:08:03,567 --> 00:08:06,153
<i>We were attacked at such
a convenient time.</i>

119
00:08:06,237 --> 00:08:09,573
<i>It's like saying that Kira is in
the Japanese Task Force Headquarters.</i>

120
00:08:09,782 --> 00:08:11,200
<i>With this in mind,</i>

121
00:08:11,283 --> 00:08:14,829
<i>you're Worse than e preschooler if
you're nol' suspicious of the Second L .</i>

122
00:08:15,788 --> 00:08:18,791
The number I gave the day
before is working again,

123
00:08:18,916 --> 00:08:20,710
so call any time you like.

124
00:08:21,627 --> 00:08:23,504
<i>Well, then...
I'll be waiting.</i>

125
00:08:30,052 --> 00:08:33,347
He's pretty sure of himself.
Near's pretty bold.

126
00:08:36,350 --> 00:08:40,688
Everyone, help Near if you want to.

127
00:08:41,564 --> 00:08:44,316
I'm not satisfied with this situation.

128
00:08:44,984 --> 00:08:49,864
Ideally, we should be
cooperating with the SPK.

129
00:08:50,489 --> 00:08:53,075
Near is tripping us up, isn't he?

130
00:09:17,475 --> 00:09:19,351
<i>When I think about...</i>

131
00:09:19,518 --> 00:09:21,687
<i>Deputy Director Yagami,
I don't want to suspect Light.</i>

132
00:09:22,396 --> 00:09:23,522
<i>But...</i>

133
00:09:24,273 --> 00:09:25,316
Dad?

134
00:09:26,692 --> 00:09:29,111
Welcome back.
So you're home today.

135
00:09:29,820 --> 00:09:31,989
Yeah... You're still awake?

136
00:09:32,490 --> 00:09:33,949
I have exams coming up...

137
00:09:34,283 --> 00:09:35,326
I see.

138
00:09:35,534 --> 00:09:37,286
Don't push yourself too hard.

139
00:09:37,495 --> 00:09:39,330
Okay. You too.

140
00:09:59,642 --> 00:10:03,521
<i>It's not unusual for someone
to want t0 contact Near.</i>

141
00:10:04,230 --> 00:10:05,564
<i>The problem comes after that.</i>

142
00:10:06,690 --> 00:10:09,652
<i>If I'm late to act,
something I can't fix may happen...</i>

143
00:10:15,407 --> 00:10:16,784
<i>I have no choice but to do it!</i>

144
00:10:20,246 --> 00:10:22,581
It's an emergency order from Light.

145
00:10:25,751 --> 00:10:28,254
Umm...number three...

146
00:10:31,132 --> 00:10:32,133
Huh?

147
00:10:34,426 --> 00:10:35,427
No way...

148
00:10:39,682 --> 00:10:40,933
Yes, this is Near.

149
00:10:42,184 --> 00:10:44,603
<i>This is Aizawa of
the Japanese Task Force.</i>

150
00:10:58,868 --> 00:11:01,162
The time has finally come...

151
00:11:01,996 --> 00:11:05,875
In order to keep me safe and
for me to become a normal wife...

152
00:11:06,625 --> 00:11:08,335
This is what Light wants for me!

153
00:11:08,419 --> 00:11:11,088
He wants me to be happy
just as a woman should be...

154
00:11:11,630 --> 00:11:13,632
Light...Thank you...

155
00:11:17,469 --> 00:11:20,264
I see. How fascinating.

156
00:11:21,015 --> 00:11:23,934
So, that L was detained for more
than 5O days...

157
00:11:24,018 --> 00:11:27,813
and there were two suspects who were
cleared due to the 13-day rule.

158
00:11:29,190 --> 00:11:31,483
Of course, that alone doesn't mean
that they're Kira...

159
00:11:32,276 --> 00:11:34,570
<i>So L just simply released them?</i>

160
00:11:34,820 --> 00:11:38,073
No... I had Deputy Director Yagami,
who was Bureau Chief at the time...

161
00:11:38,199 --> 00:11:39,825
put on an act.

162
00:11:40,326 --> 00:11:44,121
He said that they both had
been found to be Kira and Second Kira...

163
00:11:44,496 --> 00:11:46,498
and were being taken to be executed...

164
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:49,668
During that, the Deputy Director...

165
00:11:50,169 --> 00:11:53,839
pointed a gun at the suspects and said
that he would kill Kira and kill himself.

166
00:11:57,092 --> 00:11:58,928
<i>We rationalized if they were Kira,</i>

167
00:11:59,011 --> 00:12:01,472
<i>they would kill the Deputy Director
if pressed that far.</i>

168
00:12:04,350 --> 00:12:06,018
<i>Kira is quite impressive...</i>

169
00:12:07,061 --> 00:12:10,397
<i>He used his detainment to
demonstrate his innocence...</i>

170
00:12:12,107 --> 00:12:16,695
<i>Did the suspect volunteer
himself to be detained?</i>

171
00:12:18,364 --> 00:12:21,617
<i>Come to think of it,
Light did volunteer to be detained...</i>

172
00:12:23,869 --> 00:12:26,205
<i>If he did,
then it's already decided...</i>

173
00:12:27,373 --> 00:12:30,542
So who is it?
Who were those two suspects?

174
00:12:32,127 --> 00:12:33,170
I can't tell you that much.

175
00:12:33,796 --> 00:12:37,716
I'm still a member of the Japanese
Task Force and am working under L.

176
00:12:38,926 --> 00:12:40,010
<i>I understand.</i>

177
00:12:40,928 --> 00:12:43,389
Thank you very much for
your valuable information.

178
00:12:43,722 --> 00:12:45,557
Especially the part about
the Shinigami eyes

179
00:12:45,641 --> 00:12:47,601
that enable people
to see other's names.

180
00:12:47,685 --> 00:12:49,895
<i>It's the first I've heard of it.
It will be helpful. Good bye.</i>

181
00:12:58,070 --> 00:13:01,115
Is it all right? Near, shouldn't you
have pressed a little more?

182
00:13:01,824 --> 00:13:06,161
I think that his cooperation with us
is fine at this rate. Also...

183
00:13:06,662 --> 00:13:08,414
I discovered
something very important...

184
00:13:10,541 --> 00:13:11,667
Deputy Director Yagami and the person

185
00:13:11,750 --> 00:13:14,503
who is suspected of being Kira
are parent and child.

186
00:13:15,796 --> 00:13:17,089
That's the only thing it could be.

187
00:13:17,715 --> 00:13:21,302
It's the only reason he would say
that he would kill Kira and kill himself...

188
00:13:23,262 --> 00:13:24,305
Therefore...

189
00:13:24,471 --> 00:13:28,434
The Second L, and the one
who I think is Kira, is...

190
00:13:30,519 --> 00:13:31,687
Light Yagami.

191
00:13:40,779 --> 00:13:41,780
Light.

192
00:13:42,281 --> 00:13:43,282
Yes.

193
00:13:43,991 --> 00:13:46,910
I'm going to tell you the truth.
I contacted Near.

194
00:13:52,458 --> 00:13:53,667
Don't worry about it.

195
00:13:54,752 --> 00:13:58,297
I suggested it...
So what did you say?

196
00:13:59,173 --> 00:14:00,174
Oh...

197
00:14:00,841 --> 00:14:05,763
No, I won't ask. It was strange of me
to ask about that.

198
00:14:08,849 --> 00:14:11,518
I want to believe that
you're not Kira...

199
00:14:12,436 --> 00:14:14,355
Sorry for doing this again,

200
00:14:14,813 --> 00:14:17,316
but I want to observe you until
we catch Kira.

201
00:14:18,192 --> 00:14:19,860
And Misa Amane as well.

202
00:14:20,819 --> 00:14:22,738
I'm going to check your room
right now.

203
00:14:23,405 --> 00:14:25,824
There's a possibility that Amane
has a notebook.

204
00:14:26,325 --> 00:14:27,659
Hold on, Mr. Aizawa!

205
00:14:28,118 --> 00:14:30,829
No, go right ahead.
You can prove to everyone that...

206
00:14:30,913 --> 00:14:34,666
I'm not sneaking around
and contacting Misa.

207
00:14:49,932 --> 00:14:50,933
<i>Mogi...</i>

208
00:14:51,183 --> 00:14:53,310
I also want to make sure.

209
00:14:58,399 --> 00:15:01,026
<i>It would be best if
Light isn't Kira, but...</i>

210
00:15:02,027 --> 00:15:05,197
<i>If Amane has any evidence
linking her to Kira...</i>

211
00:15:06,031 --> 00:15:07,116
<i>If that happens...</i>

212
00:15:35,269 --> 00:15:37,062
Oh! Mochi and Monchichi!

213
00:15:37,563 --> 00:15:39,064
It's been a while.

214
00:15:39,815 --> 00:15:42,568
Light hasn't come back because
of the Kira investigation

215
00:15:42,693 --> 00:15:43,861
so I've been so bored.

216
00:15:44,778 --> 00:15:48,115
<i>It's impossible for her to have the notebook
on her while dressed like that...</i>

217
00:15:49,074 --> 00:15:53,036
We were just told that there
were explosives planted at L's house.

218
00:15:53,454 --> 00:15:55,247
We think it's a prank,
but we'd still like to check the room...

219
00:15:55,414 --> 00:15:58,667
What?! ls Light all right?
I've got to call him.

220
00:15:58,834 --> 00:16:00,043
You can't.

221
00:16:00,461 --> 00:16:01,462
Why?

222
00:16:01,795 --> 00:16:03,046
Light is all right.

223
00:16:03,630 --> 00:16:06,717
He's busy with something right now,

224
00:16:06,800 --> 00:16:08,677
so he handed the investigation to us.

225
00:16:09,511 --> 00:16:10,679
I guess so.

226
00:16:10,762 --> 00:16:15,726
Light loves me very much, so he'd
probably just worry if he heard my voice.

227
00:16:16,477 --> 00:16:18,937
<i>Search as much
as you like, Aizawa...</i>

228
00:16:20,272 --> 00:16:21,565
<i>You won't find the notebook...</i>

229
00:16:32,493 --> 00:16:35,621
I don't want all this to ruin
the mood we have here.

230
00:16:36,121 --> 00:16:40,334
We're not in a club.
You and Mogi should do as you see fit.

231
00:16:43,962 --> 00:16:46,381
Oh. It's time for Kira's Kingdom.

232
00:16:48,842 --> 00:16:51,386
KIRA'S KINGDOM

233
00:16:52,721 --> 00:16:58,185
<i>Hello, supporters of Kira.
I am Demegawa, the voice of Kira.</i>

234
00:16:58,977 --> 00:17:04,107
<i>Take a look. Kira's Kingdom
